<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #8B4513;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 30px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .alert {
        background-color: #fee;
        border: 1px solid #fcc;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        background-color: #8B4513;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #666;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Payment Issue with Your Subscription</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @customer.full_name %>,</p>
        
        <div class="alert">
          <strong>⚠️ Payment Failed</strong><br>
          We were unable to process your payment for your <%= @plan.name %> subscription.
        </div>
        
        <p>
          <% if @failed_count == 1 %>
            This is the first time we've had trouble processing your payment. Don't worry - we'll try again automatically.
          <% elsif @failed_count == 2 %>
            We've now attempted to charge your payment method twice without success. We'll make one more automatic attempt.
          <% elsif @failed_count >= 3 %>
            We've made <%= @failed_count %> attempts to charge your payment method without success. Your subscription may be suspended soon.
          <% end %>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <strong>What you can do:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Check that your payment method has sufficient funds</li>
          <li>Verify that your card hasn't expired</li>
          <li>Update your payment method if needed</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <%= link_to "Update Payment Method", @update_payment_url, class: "button" %>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>
          Best regards,<br>
          The Coffee Subscription Team
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          You're receiving this email because you have an active coffee subscription.<br>
          If you believe this is a mistake, please contact us immediately.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
